WEBVTT

01:45.280 --> 01:46.200
Back then,

01:47.360 --> 01:49.800
I severed my spiritual tail
in one desperate gamble

01:51.000 --> 01:52.240
and nearly died.

01:53.160 --> 01:54.440
When I was at death's door,

01:54.520 --> 01:56.320
it was Master Dragon Deity who saved me.

01:58.200 --> 01:59.920
He granted me a portion

02:00.440 --> 02:02.040
of his own Dragon Deity's Power,

02:03.560 --> 02:05.320
and that's how I survived.

02:06.720 --> 02:07.880
So,

02:09.039 --> 02:10.520
we made a pact.

02:11.280 --> 02:13.120
I lent out the nine-tailed power

02:15.040 --> 02:17.080
and swore to protect
the Dragon Deity forever.

02:24.600 --> 02:26.120
And yet you still broke the pact.

02:27.200 --> 02:29.560
Yuan Wuhuo is truly vicious.

02:30.360 --> 02:32.320
He stirred up murders and panic,

02:32.400 --> 02:35.200
shook the people's faith
in Master Dragon Deity,

02:35.720 --> 02:37.440
and used that chance to weaken his power.

02:38.200 --> 02:40.480
As the goodness
in people's hearts is eroded

02:40.560 --> 02:43.360
and malice begins to grow,
Jiu Ying's power

02:43.960 --> 02:45.320
grows stronger and stronger.

02:45.920 --> 02:47.400
When the Dragon Deity falls,

02:47.480 --> 02:49.320
Jiu Ying will break free of his seal

02:49.400 --> 02:51.160
and return to this world.

03:02.040 --> 03:05.640
You've been stalling us
to buy time for those two.

03:06.160 --> 03:08.680
Wangyan,
they're trying to take Xiaowei away.

03:12.360 --> 03:16.200
Shiguang, are you planning
to snatch him by force?

03:17.440 --> 03:19.040
Now that you've seen through it,

03:20.080 --> 03:21.160
you're staying here,

03:21.240 --> 03:22.480
whether you want to or not.

03:24.000 --> 03:25.720
Under normal circumstances,

03:25.800 --> 03:27.160
if you wanted me to stay,

03:27.240 --> 03:28.840
I'd be more than happy to.

03:28.920 --> 03:30.240
But today,

03:30.320 --> 03:32.680
I'm afraid you won't be able to keep me.

04:11.520 --> 04:13.280
Wangyan, are you all right?

04:14.880 --> 04:16.000
I'm fine.

04:18.440 --> 04:20.079
You hurt my sister?

04:20.720 --> 04:22.720
I'll make you bleed too!

04:54.960 --> 04:58.640
GOLDEN WEAVE

04:59.240 --> 05:00.120
Xiaowei,

05:00.760 --> 05:03.640
you broke your vow
and took innocent lives.

05:03.720 --> 05:06.880
I'm taking you back
to the Shilin Sect now to face judgment.

05:14.560 --> 05:16.640
The Dragon Deity's Power inside you

05:17.160 --> 05:19.240
can dispel all curses

05:19.760 --> 05:21.640
and bring the dead back to life.

05:21.720 --> 05:23.600
Use it to save Yu Shengwei.

05:24.200 --> 05:24.960
The butterfly demon.

05:25.560 --> 05:26.560
The butterfly demon?

05:37.200 --> 05:38.240
Save her.

05:38.320 --> 05:40.120
Save her.

05:40.200 --> 05:42.080
Bring Wang Sheng back.

05:43.080 --> 05:44.800
Don't you want to repay your debt?

05:47.000 --> 05:49.520
Only you can save her now.

06:05.160 --> 06:06.240
Stop!

06:18.960 --> 06:21.200
That butterfly demon
is stealing the Dragon Deity's Power.

06:22.480 --> 06:24.520
Liu Weixue, stop!

07:21.360 --> 07:22.200
Dragon scales?

08:22.040 --> 08:26.240
I didn't expect there'd be
a double-flower hunter here too.

09:26.480 --> 09:29.920
A double-flower hunter
is as formidable as I thought.

10:03.920 --> 10:05.560
Ji Ling, come here!

10:45.680 --> 10:46.920
Ji Ling!

10:55.200 --> 10:56.480
-Ji Ling!
-Back off!

11:03.720 --> 11:04.760
Ji…

11:37.400 --> 11:39.320
It seems he can no longer suppress
the demon power inside him.

11:39.400 --> 11:41.920
-He's about to lose control.
-That's not demon power.

12:13.080 --> 12:14.400
What happened to the Ice Curse?

12:15.560 --> 12:19.440
Why can he use his power so recklessly
without being hunted?

12:19.520 --> 12:21.320
He's using the Dragon Deity's Power.

12:21.840 --> 12:23.480
Naturally, it won't trigger the Ice Curse.

12:24.400 --> 12:25.720
Dragon Deity's Power?

12:26.560 --> 12:28.640
How could Xiaowei
have the Dragon Deity's Power?

12:31.480 --> 12:32.240
Commander Li.

12:36.080 --> 12:36.880
Ji Ling?

13:10.680 --> 13:11.520
Demon marks?

13:24.200 --> 13:27.320
Wangyan, Xiaowei's power
is completely out of control.

13:27.400 --> 13:28.240
What do we do?

13:28.320 --> 13:29.560
Only the Dragon Deity can deal with him.

13:30.440 --> 13:32.280
But he's in the Shilin Sect.

13:32.360 --> 13:33.840
He'd never come
to the Wei mansion for Xiaowei.

13:33.920 --> 13:36.080
Then we'll bring Xiaowei
to the Dragon Deity.

13:36.160 --> 13:37.280
Hold him off.

13:37.800 --> 13:39.360
I'll take Ms. Yu
to the Dragon Deity Temple.

14:19.040 --> 14:20.600
Master Dragon Deity,

14:21.480 --> 14:22.800
he was gravely wounded by Xiaowei,

14:23.960 --> 14:24.960
and now,

14:25.720 --> 14:26.560
he's beyond saving.

15:08.360 --> 15:09.360
Dispose of him.

15:11.240 --> 15:12.240
Yes.

16:13.360 --> 16:14.400
Out of the way!

16:16.120 --> 16:16.960
Out of the way!

16:19.120 --> 16:20.080
Out of the way!

16:40.120 --> 16:41.120
A barrier?

16:44.120 --> 16:45.000
Do you have a death wish?

16:45.080 --> 16:46.640
This barrier was set
with the Dragon Deity's Power.

16:46.720 --> 16:48.080
It'll kill you!

16:49.160 --> 16:50.160
Give her back to me!

16:58.840 --> 16:59.880
Take her.

17:30.240 --> 17:31.320
That brat

17:32.640 --> 17:33.880
sure knows how to play dirty.

17:50.640 --> 17:51.440
Brilliant.

17:59.880 --> 18:01.040
The barrier

18:01.960 --> 18:02.920
has been broken.

18:04.520 --> 18:05.680
How could that happen?

18:08.280 --> 18:10.360
Xiaowei carries the Dragon Deity's Power.

18:11.440 --> 18:13.320
Naturally, he can destroy the barrier.

18:14.120 --> 18:16.520
Master, stay here.

18:17.120 --> 18:18.440
I'll deal with Xiaowei.

18:29.240 --> 18:30.160
Wu Shiguang!

18:53.600 --> 18:54.440
Don't be afraid.

18:55.560 --> 18:56.760
I'll bring you back right now.

19:12.240 --> 19:13.200
Wangyan,

19:13.880 --> 19:15.640
he's using the Dragon Deity's Power.

19:15.720 --> 19:17.600
Xiaowei, Ms. Yu's injuries are too severe.

19:17.680 --> 19:19.160
She can't be saved.

19:19.240 --> 19:21.320
Using the Dragon Deity's Power
to forcibly reverse life and death

19:21.400 --> 19:22.680
goes against the laws of heaven.

19:23.240 --> 19:24.920
You'll be reduced to ashes too!

19:25.440 --> 19:26.360
I don't care!

19:28.440 --> 19:30.040
Well, I do.

19:40.600 --> 19:41.480
Wangyan.

19:47.720 --> 19:50.960
How dare you demons
barge into the Dragon Deity Temple?

19:57.440 --> 19:58.280
Word Magic?

19:58.800 --> 19:59.760
Stay on guard.

20:05.440 --> 20:07.440
Piercing frost,

20:09.040 --> 20:11.360
let utter darkness descend.

20:31.480 --> 20:33.760
Why… Why can't I see?

20:42.680 --> 20:43.680
Wangyan…

20:48.040 --> 20:49.080
Steady your mind.

20:49.160 --> 20:50.520
Don't let Xiaowei control you.

20:59.520 --> 21:02.360
Xiaowei's Word Magic really is formidable.

21:15.120 --> 21:16.520
Li Jie isn't affected?

21:17.520 --> 21:20.760
It seems Li Jie's physical cultivation
is anything but ordinary.

21:21.520 --> 21:23.200
No wonder he could fight us blow for blow,

21:23.720 --> 21:26.680
with nothing but that long blade,
without relying on sacred power.

21:27.760 --> 21:28.920
That man is not to be taken lightly.

21:35.920 --> 21:37.440
We can't let him kill Xiaowei.

21:37.960 --> 21:39.600
Wuyi, let's go.

21:47.440 --> 21:49.920
As expected,
the three foxes have joined forces.

22:08.320 --> 22:09.200
Wuyi!

22:44.280 --> 22:47.360
Eastern Purple Lightning,
grant me your power.

23:23.280 --> 23:24.160
Wangyan!

24:13.760 --> 24:16.800
-Wuyi.
-Wangyan, I'm fine.

24:25.440 --> 24:28.040
Greetings, Master Dragon Deity!

24:47.120 --> 24:48.320
The Dragon Deity?

24:48.840 --> 24:51.880
Wangyan,
that wasn't the Dragon Deity's Power.

24:51.960 --> 24:54.280
It was the Eastern Purple Lightning
from the high-rank demon Bai Ze.

24:54.360 --> 24:57.600
Bai Ze knows the weaknesses of all demons.

24:57.680 --> 24:59.920
Under the Eastern Purple Lightning,

25:00.000 --> 25:03.120
no demon can hide or escape pursuit.

25:04.760 --> 25:07.000
No wonder he didn't strike
those demon hunters

25:07.080 --> 25:08.240
and only attacked us.

25:09.680 --> 25:11.240
Looks like the rumors were true.

25:15.640 --> 25:18.520
But why did he attack Wu Shiguang too?

25:36.080 --> 25:37.200
Xiaowei,

25:38.720 --> 25:40.200
you've committed a grave crime.

25:41.880 --> 25:42.960
I know.

25:43.920 --> 25:46.240
But I have to save her.

25:47.200 --> 25:50.280
The Dragon Deity's Power
is meant to save all living beings.

25:51.280 --> 25:52.920
It cannot be used for one person alone.

25:55.680 --> 25:57.520
Having been granted
the Dragon Deity's Power,

25:57.600 --> 26:00.320
I swear never to claim it for myself,
never to use it for evil,

26:01.280 --> 26:03.160
but only to protect all living beings.

26:03.240 --> 26:05.040
If I break this oath,

26:05.120 --> 26:08.200
may I be shattered to pieces
and doomed forever.

26:19.280 --> 26:21.360
Even if I'm shattered to pieces

26:21.440 --> 26:22.960
and doomed forever,

26:23.920 --> 26:25.680
I must save her.

27:43.000 --> 27:44.280
Stubborn fool.

27:49.840 --> 27:51.320
Everything you said by my bedside

27:51.840 --> 27:54.560
while I was unconscious…

27:56.040 --> 27:57.360
I heard it all.

27:58.920 --> 28:00.280
For hundreds of years,

28:02.240 --> 28:03.880
through life after life,

28:05.440 --> 28:07.800
all I've ever wanted was to keep you safe.

28:09.280 --> 28:10.480
But now,

28:11.920 --> 28:13.400
I've only hurt you.

28:18.200 --> 28:19.480
I never knew

28:19.560 --> 28:23.240
the chestnut cakes were made by you.

28:24.400 --> 28:27.560
I've felt your heart.

28:29.320 --> 28:32.200
Can you grant me one wish?

28:32.280 --> 28:33.520
Yes, of course.

28:34.040 --> 28:37.000
Whatever it takes, even if I'm torn apart,

28:37.520 --> 28:39.200
I'll keep my word.

28:41.320 --> 28:42.400
Let me…

28:44.320 --> 28:45.600
go.

28:47.240 --> 28:51.640
Use your power to save more people.

28:53.240 --> 28:57.640
The people of Luo'an are waiting for you.

28:57.720 --> 28:58.600
No…

28:59.160 --> 29:00.160
No!

29:00.240 --> 29:02.280
No…

29:02.360 --> 29:03.880
I don't want to!

29:05.720 --> 29:08.800
Grant me this final wish.

29:08.880 --> 29:11.280
No, I don't want to.

29:11.360 --> 29:12.560
No…

29:26.760 --> 29:28.320
Dragon hearts as one,

29:29.200 --> 29:30.680
all to source return,

29:36.920 --> 29:38.960
all barriers break.

29:53.800 --> 29:54.880
Th…

29:55.520 --> 29:57.000
Thank you.

30:19.160 --> 30:20.200
You were nothing but a pawn.

30:20.280 --> 30:21.000
FOURTEENTH YEAR OF THE ZHENYUAN ERA

30:21.080 --> 30:24.000
Every word I ever said to you was a lie.

30:24.520 --> 30:25.680
But you refused to believe it.

30:26.200 --> 30:29.160
Your heart is filled with nothing
but your own obsession.

30:30.960 --> 30:32.200
My heart has long belonged to the Buddha.

30:32.280 --> 30:33.120
TWENTIETH YEAR OF THE SHENGJING ERA

30:33.200 --> 30:34.080
I carry no more attachments.

30:35.560 --> 30:37.040
Let go of your obsession.

30:46.880 --> 30:49.480
NINETEENTH YEAR OF THE CHANGYUN ERA

31:26.080 --> 31:29.720
The Wang Sheng who gave his life
to save you died long ago.

31:30.280 --> 31:32.280
You've been searching for him
for hundreds of years,

31:32.800 --> 31:34.240
life after life.

31:34.960 --> 31:36.800
But we're not who you're looking for.

31:37.520 --> 31:39.440
You used your Formless Moon mark

31:39.520 --> 31:41.680
to mark them in the vast sea of people

31:42.200 --> 31:43.480
so you could find them.

31:44.000 --> 31:45.280
But in truth,

31:45.800 --> 31:47.960
they were all just strangers
passing through your life.

31:53.440 --> 31:55.680
You said you were looking for Wang Sheng,

31:56.200 --> 31:58.240
that you wanted to repay his kindness.

31:59.520 --> 32:00.840
But really,

32:01.360 --> 32:04.880
you're only trapped
by an obsession you refuse to let go of.

32:23.440 --> 32:24.880
Kites for sale!

32:24.960 --> 32:26.400
All kinds of kites!

32:27.600 --> 32:29.840
Miss, would you like to take a look?

32:32.880 --> 32:34.240
See if any one catches your eye.

33:57.400 --> 33:59.080
A lifetime is filled

34:00.600 --> 34:02.160
with all eight kinds of suffering.

34:05.240 --> 34:06.880
But in this life of mine,

34:08.520 --> 34:10.040
I have only this one suffering.

34:11.880 --> 34:12.960
There is no cure for it

34:14.360 --> 34:16.159
and no one to resent for it.

34:22.040 --> 34:23.719
Perhaps before long,

34:24.639 --> 34:26.600
you too will follow in my footsteps.

34:28.320 --> 34:29.679
Don't.

34:31.159 --> 34:32.400
It's not worth it.

35:49.280 --> 35:51.320
The Dragon Deity's Power
I granted you back then

35:51.400 --> 35:53.840
has long since merged with your souls.

35:55.080 --> 35:58.600
If you return it,
you'll lose all your power.

35:59.400 --> 36:00.560
If returning it can seal Jiu Ying

36:00.640 --> 36:02.080
and save all living beings,

36:02.800 --> 36:04.560
we are willing to die.

36:05.080 --> 36:07.040
None of you needs to sacrifice yourselves.

36:07.560 --> 36:08.680
I have another way.

36:10.040 --> 36:12.640
You need only lend me your demon power.

36:13.160 --> 36:14.920
As for reclaiming my sacred power,

36:15.000 --> 36:17.920
I have other plans for that in the future.

36:32.320 --> 36:33.160
Bai Ze,

36:33.680 --> 36:34.800
Han Ba,

36:35.320 --> 36:36.560
Wu Zhiqi,

36:37.320 --> 36:38.520
and Xiaowei,

36:39.280 --> 36:41.560
I hope you will keep your promise

36:41.640 --> 36:44.600
and protect the Dragon Deity forever.

37:13.920 --> 37:15.200
Take him back to the Shilin Sect.

37:15.800 --> 37:16.600
Yes, Master.

37:40.000 --> 37:41.200
Ji Ling!

38:27.120 --> 38:28.840
Ji Ling? Ji Ling!

38:29.760 --> 38:30.680
Chi Wen!

38:50.840 --> 38:52.040
‎SERVE THE SCALES, UPHOLD THE RIGHT

38:55.280 --> 38:56.160
I'm saved!

38:56.880 --> 38:57.720
I'm going home!

38:57.800 --> 38:59.120
-I've come to my senses!
-Thank you, Dragon Deity!

38:59.200 --> 39:01.160
-I'm going home!
-She's saved.

39:01.240 --> 39:02.320
My daughter is saved!

39:02.400 --> 39:03.840
Thank you, Dragon Deity!

39:03.920 --> 39:04.880
Thank you, Dragon Deity!

39:07.160 --> 39:10.720
Xiaowei was trapped by his own obsession.

39:11.440 --> 39:13.800
What about you? Do you have an obsession?

39:14.880 --> 39:16.280
I think

39:16.800 --> 39:19.080
an obsession is like the simplest

39:19.160 --> 39:20.800
and most complicated riddle in the world.

39:21.320 --> 39:22.480
I probably don't have one.

39:23.000 --> 39:26.960
At most, I just want to find
the sweetest raspberry

39:27.040 --> 39:28.720
in a whole patch full of them.

39:30.160 --> 39:32.080
What about you, Master Dragon Deity?

39:32.600 --> 39:35.240
Obsession is like searching
in endless darkness

39:35.960 --> 39:37.680
for a single night

39:39.720 --> 39:41.520
or searching
in a boundless sea of suffering

39:42.800 --> 39:44.920
for a single drop of water
untouched by bitterness.

40:00.960 --> 40:03.760
SERVE THE SCALES, UPHOLD THE RIGHT

40:13.960 --> 40:15.360
Chasing an obsession,

40:16.360 --> 40:17.800
worn down by the years,

40:18.680 --> 40:20.480
and trapped in a self-made prison…

40:25.520 --> 40:26.760
What a pity,

40:29.080 --> 40:30.400
Xiaowei.

41:23.120 --> 41:24.560
Keeping a secret

41:25.760 --> 41:27.680
is like guarding a fragile candle flame.

41:29.640 --> 41:33.200
And so, you have no choice
but to tell lie after lie.

41:39.400 --> 41:41.160
ALL FLOURISH FOR THE SCALES

41:42.680 --> 41:45.480
SERVE THE SCALES, UPHOLD THE RIGHT

41:55.080 --> 41:57.440
Don't you think
the Dragon Deity and Ji Ling

41:58.040 --> 41:59.440
look a lot alike?

42:00.400 --> 42:02.440
-Don't talk nonsense.
-Could Ji Ling be an illegitimate son?

42:02.520 --> 42:03.640
Nonsense!

42:03.720 --> 42:06.200
The nine dragon sons
all have names and titles.

42:06.280 --> 42:07.760
How could there be an illegitimate son?

42:24.320 --> 42:25.680
Misses, need a boat?

42:27.320 --> 42:28.320
Watch your step.

42:44.720 --> 42:45.640
Oh, no.

43:02.040 --> 43:02.880
Master Chi Wen,

43:02.960 --> 43:05.040
the two stone beasts have been restored,

43:05.120 --> 43:08.000
but the barrier can't be reactivated
without the Dragon Deity's Power.

43:09.400 --> 43:11.760
The barrier of the two stone beasts
at the main gate

43:11.840 --> 43:13.320
only strips demons of their disguise.

43:14.480 --> 43:16.280
The Shilin Sect itself
is covered in ancient formations

43:16.360 --> 43:18.880
powerful enough
to destroy demons body and soul.

43:18.960 --> 43:20.040
There's no need to worry.

43:24.880 --> 43:26.400
I'm not worried about myself.

43:29.000 --> 43:30.280
What worries me

43:33.520 --> 43:35.120
is the Dragon Deity's Power

43:35.200 --> 43:36.920
still loose out there.

45:46.480 --> 45:47.880
You've crossed the line.
